    "section_rich_text_e6mjYe": {
      "type": "section-rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_jwY6kg": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "A Wardrobe That Feels Like You",
            "heading_font_size": "heading-large",
            "padding_bottom": 16,
            "heading_tag": "automatic"
          }
        },
        "text_x6zNVy": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We believe clothes are more than fabric — they’re memories in the making. Each piece we design is meant to slip effortlessly into your life, becoming the dress you reach for on a Sunday stroll, the blazer that carries you from desk to dinner, the knit you’ll still love years from now.</p>",
            "text_font_size": "body-medium",
            "padding_bottom": 16
          }
        },
        "text_xCR9DK": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Fashion should feel personal. Romantic, but never fussy. Confident, but never loud. We create timeless silhouettes with a modern spirit — garments that highlight the woman rather than overshadow her. Inspired by the ease of Parisian style, our collections are built around pieces that celebrate femininity in all its forms.</p>",
            "text_font_size": "body-medium",
            "padding_bottom": 16
          }
        },
        "text_U7dF44": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>From the curve of a neckline to the drape of a sleeve, every detail matters. Our prints are designed in-house, our fabrics carefully chosen, our cuts refined to flatter and move with you. We work in small runs, with trusted European ateliers, ensuring quality that lasts beyond seasons.</p>",
            "text_font_size": "body-medium",
            "padding_bottom": 16
          }
        },
        "divider_kcKMkD": {
          "type": "divider",
          "settings": {
            "show_line": true,
            "padding_bottom": 20
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_jwY6kg",
